name: Denham Reagh EP
description:
The bands debut 'self-titled' release. Recorded at A#Studios and dwhmedia respectively it showcases the bands unique songwriting and lyrical integrity. Including ballads, pop and alternative rock this 5 track EP is sure to have something for everyone.

TRACKLISTING
1. Remember When
2. City Lights
3. On Your Own
4. Moving On
5. Turn To You

name: Rock 4 Life International Vol 7
description: Benefit CD to raise awareness of PSC (Primary Aclerosing Cholangitis). Visit www.pscpartners.org for more information. Released April 2009 through Quickstar Productions it features unsigned artists from all over the world. Includes our song On Your Own.
